## Introduction

This is a Markdown file just with a few Tcl code chunks.

## Hello World

```{.tcl}
puts "Hello Tcl World!"
```

## Variable Values

```{.tcl}
set x 1
puts $x
```

In the next code chunk we increment x:

```{.tcl}
incr x
puts $x
```

## Inline code evaluation

The value of x is `tcl set x`!

